<p>Got it. To do that, you'll need to change these things:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Show&nbsp;Code</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Hide&nbsp;code</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<div class="hl-main">
<pre>
<span class="hl-special">:root</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-brackets">{</span><span class="hl-code">
     --</span><span class="hl-reserved">header-subtitle:</span><span class="hl-code"> &quot;特异 事故 办公处&quot;</span><span class="hl-code">;
</span><span class="hl-brackets">}</span><span class="hl-code">
 
</span><span class="hl-identifier">#header</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">h2</span><span class="hl-code">, </span><span class="hl-identifier">#header</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">h2</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">span</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-brackets">{</span><span class="hl-code">
     </span><span class="hl-reserved">width:</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-number">21</span><span class="hl-code">rem</span><span class="hl-code">;
</span><span class="hl-brackets">}</span><span class="hl-code">
 
</span><span class="hl-var">@media</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">only</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">screen</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">and</span><span class="hl-code"> (max-width: 768</span><span class="hl-identifier">px</span><span class="hl-code">) </span><span class="hl-brackets">{</span><span class="hl-code">
    </span><span class="hl-identifier">#header</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">h2</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-identifier">span</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-brackets">{</span><span class="hl-code">
         </span><span class="hl-reserved">width:</span><span class="hl-code"> </span><span class="hl-number">6</span><span class="hl-code">rem</span><span class="hl-code">;
    </span><span class="hl-brackets">}</span><span class="hl-code">
</span><span class="hl-brackets">}</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Essentially, the wrapping of the words depends on the width of the <tt>#header h2 span</tt>. I really need to go in to BHL and redo how the Title and Subtitle are place, though. They're really irritating and cumbersome to deal with.</p>
<hr />
<p>Oh! Also, I added some styling to fix the scp-number text on the sidebar. It's yellow on the Chinese branch atm and it doesn't look great. I forgot about it since the EN branch removed them :p</p>

